title: Graylog: License
agents: graylog
catalog: app/graylog
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the state of the license used with a Graylog instance. It
 outputs the expired, violated and valid state, if the traffic limit is
 exceeded, if the cluster is not covered and if nodes exceeded. Furthermore it
 reports if remote checks failed, the traffic limit, the time until the license
 expires and informational, the subject of the license, if license is a trial
 and if it requires remote checks.

 Needs the datasource "Check state of Graylog" to be configured.

inventory:
 One service is created.
